snippet.title: HarleQuest! Demo 2.5 Gameplay - now with music and sound effects!
snippet.description:
Everyone was asking for sound in the last demo build, so here it is :D You can grab an updated build from here: https://t.co/K2tSwin6gD

Or grab your free physical copy of Debug Indie Sampler #2 from here: https://www.wavegamestudios.com/shop/debug-indie-sampler-2

Enjoy!
